form-element.label: This form Tests Paragraph and Text Inputs
form-element.instructions:
Text: should be empty, saves into multipleText
Paragraph: should be empty, saves into multipleParagraph
Phone: comes from hardcoded values in the "default value" field (value="(111)222-3333;(444)555-6666;(777)888-9999")
Should not be visible: if you can see this column in runtime, the setting of visibility from an expression is broken
Text (start): Comes from multipleText and should be read only
Paragraph (start): Comes from pv!multipleParagraph entered in the start form and should be read only

If no values were entered in the start form, the grid should have 3 rows (due to the phone values). Enter appropriate values and submit the form.
